title: Strawberry Shortcake - Her Very First Adventure
description: Strawberry Shortcake is the star of the show in this pair of vintage animated adventures that originally aired on television in the 1980s. "The World of Strawberry Shortcake" introduces first-time fans to the sweet-smelling characters of Strawberry Land. Then, in "Strawberry Shortcake in Big Apple City," Strawberry and her friends travel to compete against the Peculiar Purple Pieman of Porcupine Peak in a televised bakeoff.
